11 Chagocchaka, Kusalattika
Chagocchaka, Kusalattika
54.
142Nosaññojanaṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe…  nanosaññojanaṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
143Hetuyā nava…pe…  vipāke ekaṃ…pe…  avigate nava.
55.
144Noganthaṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe…  nooghaṃ…pe…  noyogaṃ…pe…  nonīvaraṇaṃ. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā nava…pe…  vipāke ekaṃ…pe…  avigate nava.
145Noparāmāsaṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā pañca…pe…  vipāke ekaṃ…pe…  avigate pañca.
